<emphasis id="B94DEAF0FFF16A121053F9B0FCF7D616" bold="true" box="[846,858,1635,1652]" pageId="48" pageNumber="157">E</emphasis>
, New Caledonia; 
<emphasis id="B94DEAF0FFF16A1210EDF9B0FC50D616" bold="true" box="[1008,1021,1635,1652]" pageId="48" pageNumber="157">A</emphasis>
, 
<emphasis id="B94DEAF0FFF16A12171AF9B0FBB9D616" bold="true" box="[1031,1044,1635,1652]" pageId="48" pageNumber="157">B</emphasis>
, exterior of left and right valves; 
<emphasis id="B94DEAF0FFF16A1213C4F9AAFF4AD6E8" bold="true" box="[217,231,1657,1674]" pageId="48" pageNumber="157">C</emphasis>
, 
<emphasis id="B94DEAF0FFF16A1213ECF9AAFF52D6E8" bold="true" box="[241,255,1657,1674]" pageId="48" pageNumber="157">D</emphasis>
, interior of right and left valves; 
<emphasis id="B94DEAF0FFF16A121118F9AAFDBCD6E8" bold="true" box="[517,529,1657,1674]" pageId="48" pageNumber="157">E</emphasis>
, right valve, Touho,stn 2049, New Caledonia (MNHN); 
<emphasis id="B94DEAF0FFF16A1210C8F9AAFC4DD6E8" bold="true" box="[981,992,1657,1674]" pageId="48" pageNumber="157">F</emphasis>
, 
<emphasis id="B94DEAF0FFF16A1210F7F9AAFC55D6E8" bold="true" box="[1002,1016,1657,1674]" pageId="48" pageNumber="157">G</emphasis>
, hinges of left and right valves of holotype. Scale bars: A-E, 5 mm; F, G, 2 mm.
</paragraph>
